### ============================================
### Payment Service API (Port 8082)
### ============================================
### 결제 처리 및 검증


### ------------------------------------------
### 결제 처리
### ------------------------------------------

### 새 결제 생성
POST http://localhost:8082/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "RES-001",
  "amount": 150000,
  "currency": "KRW",
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "cardExpiry": "12/25",
  "cardCvv": "123"
}

###

### 결제 상태 조회
GET http://localhost:8082/v1/payments/PAY-001
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------
### 결제 취소/환불
### ------------------------------------------

### 결제 취소
POST http://localhost:8082/v1/payments/PAY-001/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer cancellation",
  "refundAmount": 150000
}

###

### 부분 환불
POST http://localhost:8082/v1/payments/PAY-001/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refundAmount": 50000,
  "reason": "Partial refund request"
}
